description: You probably know by now that I had a big crush on Ricky since the day I first saw him. So no need to say that I get very excited each time I find unseen footage of him. This week I'm pleasing myself and all his many fans with this raw version of the Gym, Sport & Sex scene we did together. It features never-seen takes, pov & cool behind-the-scenes. I can't stop watching this one as I remember why I fell in love in the first place.
series: MSKBNS0055 - Ricky's Gym, Sport & Sex Raw
title: Ricky's Gym, Sport & Sex Raw
